overview: Stepbrother Codey Steele is in bed, looking at a photo on his laptop of his sister Julia and her friend Kate wearing bikinis. With his fingers he crops the photo to just display Kate, and he starts masturbating. Julia appears at his doorway and sees him wanking off to Kate's image. Returning to her own bedroom, Julia thinks, "What does she have that I don't?", as she gazes at the same photo on her laptop. Speaking aloud, she says: "Fuck them both!".
title: What's So Special About Her?
